9725928&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/jiaweiding","text":"2025.07.04\n\n希望能通过软考高级，能将体重控制在70kg，能顺利换学区房。","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13657901","createdAt":"2025-07-04T01:30:23Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0GkU","author":"yop97i","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/128759035?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/yop97i","text":"致十年后的自己：\n\n未来的我，见字如面。\n\n当你展读这封信时，时光已悄然走过了十个年头，来到了2035年。我不知道你是在一个阳光明媚的午后，还是在一个宁静的夜晚读到它，但写下这封信的此刻，是2025年的一个夏天，我正怀着满心的憧憬和一丝丝对未知的忐忑，想象着你的生活。\n\n十年，是一个听起来很长，但也许一晃而过的数字。这十年里，你过得好吗？是否健康、快乐，眼里的光是否依旧明亮？\n\n我最最希望的，是你已经不再孤单。你是否遇到了那个对的“她”？那个我想象中，善良、有趣、能读懂你奇奇怪怪想法的女孩。你们是不是会因为一件小事笑作一团？她喜欢猫吗？你们是否已经成为了彼此最温暖的依靠？我真心希望你已经找到了那份能让灵魂安定的爱情，能有一个人与你立黄昏，问你粥可温。\n\n现在的我，正努力奋斗，希望能为你打下基础。你是否已经拥有了那套不需要太大、但足够温馨的小房子？那里是否有你亲手布置的角落，有你们一起挑选的沙发？是否还有一辆能载着你们随时出发的车子，去探索城市的周边，或者来一场说走就走的旅行？希望你已经拥有了一个真正属于自己的“家”，一个能卸下所有疲惫的港湾。\n\n对了，我们那个毛茸茸的家庭成员呢？你是否已经实现养一只猫的梦想了？它会是慵懒的橘猫，还是优雅的布偶？希望在你看书、看电影的时候，它会蜷缩在你的腿上，用轻轻的呼噜声陪伴着你。照顾一个小生命，会让你变得更柔软吧。\n\n我一直有一个环游世界的梦想，希望你没有被生活的琐碎磨灭掉这份热情。你们开始探索这个世界了吗？是看到了巴黎铁塔的璀璨，还是感受了爱琴海的浪漫？是徒步在雪山脚下，还是潜入了蔚蓝的深海？世界那么大，我希望你正牵着她的手，在世界的不同角落，创造着属于你们的独家记忆。请一定替我多看看这个美好的世界。\n\n还有一个更长远的梦想，不知道你是否还记得。我们曾约定，退休后要开一家猫咖。一个充满阳光、咖啡香和猫咪的慵懒空间。这个梦想，是你正在为之努力的目标，还是已经提上了日程的计划？我希望你从未放弃这个溫柔的梦想，它是我们对未来最安逸的期许。\n\n当然，如果生活并没有完全按照我此刻的设想去发展，也请不要苛责自己。或许你找到了另一条让你感到幸福的路，发现了比环游世界更有趣的事，或者对“家”有了不同的定义。这些都没关系。\n\n最重要的是，你快乐吗？你是否还对生活抱有热爱，对未知充满好奇？你是否依旧善良、真诚，没有变成自己曾经讨厌的模样？\n\n请别忘记，在2025年的这个夜晚，有一个年轻人，正为你描绘着这一切。请感谢他此刻的努力，也请原谅他此刻对未来的“贪心”。\n\n无论如何，希望你正过着滚烫而丰盈的人生，不负时光，不负自己。\n\n祝你，一切安好。\n\n爱你的，\n\n十年前的自己\n\n写于 2025年7月4日","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13658388","createdAt":"2025-07-04T02:52:09Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Gmn","author":"xiaohanyes","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/101844528?u=df3dcc681f0c0a759607908d55e3c03040f05789&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/xiaohanyes","text":"希望10年后的你，熟悉甚至精通多门编程语言（C++，java），同时，希望那时的你已经参与了多个github上的开源项目。","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13658535","createdAt":"2025-07-04T03:22:54Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Gng","author":"DrizzleTime","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/169802108?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/DrizzleTime","text":"希望今年暑假能把论文投出去","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13658592","createdAt":"2025-07-04T03:31:51Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0GsL","author":"jackw111","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/127837373?u=7562d07ce7ef9989c83e31b425b23770aeae0bbe&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/jackw111","text":"希望十年后的今天，我的家人朋友都健健康康，和和睦睦。我自己可以不为钱发愁\n\n2025/7/4","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13658891","createdAt":"2025-07-04T04:30:52Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0HAU","author":"JsChen2Casiku","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/41133470?u=7273a663d4207e5250b74fd715e98a509520a42f&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/JsChen2Casiku","text":"十年啊，感觉一晃而逝，人生能有几个十年呢？加油吧，佬们","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13660180","createdAt":"2025-07-04T07:33:08Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0HQ7","author":"Unreal-Null","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/63513356?u=ec72f243a951a52c2a0354704f4e15322887b70b&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/Unreal-Null","text":"2025/07/04 明年的我是怎么样的呢","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13661243","createdAt":"2025-07-04T09:04:55Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0IVR","author":"chosen1zzzz","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/198208362?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/chosen1zzzz","text":"研究生毕业了会不会进大厂呢，10年后的我会不会挣到钱呢","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13665617","createdAt":"2025-07-04T18:31:34Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Is9","author":"dlgod7","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/204118936?u=4b8ca6ee2b0619c0149af54a2e3e021968950a62&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/dlgod7","text":"致十年后的自己：所愿皆所得，找到自己的价值","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13667133","createdAt":"2025-07-05T01:50:53Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Iuz","author":"ljfo","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/218754267?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/ljfo","text":"记得刚来公司面试，领导问你为什么来我们公司，我说之前常驻外地，到年龄，该回来结婚生子了，领导说你之前好歹还在国内，来我们这你得出国了，我说我了解过了目前手头的项目，三年内应该不会出国，领导说三年后呢，我说三年后我可以出去，然后现在出来第八个年头了。\n\n其实我的梦想很简单，在家里老婆孩子还有父母常伴左右，家人健健康康，生活平平淡淡就好。","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13667251","createdAt":"2025-07-05T02:45:46Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0I2C","author":"leanb525","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/213021974?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/leanb525","text":"梦想回到20年前买房买btc","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13667714","createdAt":"2025-07-05T05:56:17Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0I8C","author":"csskrtao","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/121599647?u=24593041cc2d6cb6062a6df1e3dfaf878e2de26f&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/csskrtao","text":"十年之后期待能遇见曾经的朋友，曾经的自己","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13668098","createdAt":"2025-07-05T08:10:01Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0J8V","author":"LeonYoah","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/95527066?u=2ecf7c86fa46e315347d87f08733754641427fe3&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/LeonYoah","text":"希望10年后的自己一切顺利","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13672213","createdAt":"2025-07-06T03:30:12Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0LZv","author":"zzlibray","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/200380830?u=69502181adae8421c5ffe1c9ef00d8f5f96a8fd3&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/zzlibray","text":"2025.7.7  老婆怀孕了，不知道是男是女。\n\n只希望未来的小孩健健康康，开开心心的活着。\n\n10年后的自己应该是45岁了。一切的未知，只希望自己跟家人能平安度过这未知的10年，但心里早有预期，珍惜眼前的一切","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13678191","createdAt":"2025-07-07T01:17:16Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0O7X","author":"studymug","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23473747?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/studymug","text":"加油","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13692631","createdAt":"2025-07-08T08:11:42Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0PXk","author":"keymanlu","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/85289355?u=e6c20ae86f84f158302964b8a3846f4138164afc&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/keymanlu","text":"我在现在这个公司做了14年了，我希望还能做多10年，把我房贷还完，这10年内尽量保持身体健康，完成之前的目标，作为家里主要收入来源，真的深深感受到无形的压力。公司也是有过几次裁员的风波，但我也坚持下来了，但是随着年纪增长，我也担心支持不到下一个十年，故在这里留下个足迹，看看有没有机会10年后再来还愿吧。","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13694436","createdAt":"2025-07-08T11:01:52Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Qa1","author":"asts-top","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/155049518?u=154220ece63b05de59ad63b542766e421a2dba84&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/asts-top","text":"现在的你是一个大二学期末的学生，希望10年以后你面对现在的一切疑问与困惑都有很好的解决方法，与此同时，现在的我也会抓住所有我能看到的机会不断向上。一起加油！","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13698741","createdAt":"2025-07-08T16:48:31Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Q7E","author":"Qi-Chuan","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/73896655?u=75bd3458d86b639cb99ccc70cf0ad17d5e5792b5&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/Qi-Chuan","text":"十年前的今天，我正在备战高三。如今身边的朋友大多数已经毕业工作家庭稳定了，而我还在苦读学业中，不知未来会何去何从，甚至也不知自己想要什么。此刻我写下这些，留给十年后的自己，希望你已经找到了人生的目标并为之努力着，身体健康，开心快乐。","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13700804","createdAt":"2025-07-08T20:41:34Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0Roa","author":"Lyn6969","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/42564665?u=91e631e3fe7c4ccc5e97a4075147a8def51ca2e8&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/Lyn6969","text":"希望自己能顺利毕业，实在不想在科研上内耗了。","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13703706","createdAt":"2025-07-09T03:47:11Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0R0L","author":"faithererer","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/104252444?u=561d93e9b7846739685e58de6a4ee6efaaacf931&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/faithererer","text":"2025.07.09 刚刚毕业，即将入职，焦虑而迷茫，不知道选择是否正确，愿自己，心气永不溃散，有勇气接受逆境与不测。\n\n人生，才刚刚开始","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13704459","createdAt":"2025-07-09T05:22:35Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0UU6","author":"9075512","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/67473225?u=edd4125438859a413ab44a518b5e1e3c6b6a86fc&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/9075512","text":"留痕，嘿嘿","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13714746","createdAt":"2025-07-10T01:00:59Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0U5-","author":"sean908","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4495319?u=adba975f4664a02c109a6a1f5af1855de3fd8afe&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/sean908","text":"小时候的“梦想”是清北\n\n现在的梦想是null 😂","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13717118","createdAt":"2025-07-10T07:25:44Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0cX-","author":"longxingdeng","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/134866140?u=96bee4175986f1362e2c04b0ee0d30890754bb0b&v=4","profile":"https://github.com/longxingdeng","text":"十年奋湛","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13747710","createdAt":"2025-07-14T04:29:33Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0cjt","author":"CodingBoyLink","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/165801007?v=4","profile":"https://github.com/CodingBoyLink","text":"支持支持","url":"https://github.com/Master08s/Master08s.github.io/discussions/2#discussioncomment-13748461","createdAt":"2025-07-14T06:38:16Z"},{"id":"DC_kwDOO1oT884A0iIA","